{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"If you had caught me straight out of college"},{"time":2000,"text":"in the halls of the Vermont State House"},{"time":4000,"text":"where I was a lobbyist in training"},{"time":7000,"text":"and asked me what I was going to do with my life,"},{"time":9000,"text":"I would have told you"},{"time":11000,"text":"that I'd just passed the Hanyu Shuiping Kaoshi,"},{"time":13000,"text":"the Chinese equivalency exam,"},{"time":15000,"text":"and I was going to go study law in Beijing,"},{"time":18000,"text":"and I was going to improve U.S.-China relations"},{"time":22000,"text":"through top-down policy changes"},{"time":24000,"text":"and judicial system reforms."},{"time":26000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":29000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":31000,"text":"I had a plan,"},{"time":34000,"text":"and I never ever thought"},{"time":37000,"text":"it would have anything to do"},{"time":39000,"text":"with the banjo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43000,"text":"Little did I know"},{"time":45000,"text":"what a huge impact it would have on me one night"},{"time":47000,"text":"when I was at a party"},{"time":49000,"text":"and I heard a sound coming out of a record player"},{"time":51000,"text":"in the corner of a room."},{"time":53000,"text":"And it was Doc Watson"},{"time":55000,"text":"singing and playing \"Shady Grove.\""},{"time":58000,"text":"♫ Shady Grove, my little love ♫"},{"time":60000,"text":"♫ Shady Grove, my darlin' ♫"},{"time":62000,"text":"♫ Shady Grove, my little love ♫"},{"time":65000,"text":"♫ Going back to Harlan ♫"},{"time":69000,"text":"That sound was just so beautiful,"},{"time":72000,"text":"the sound of Doc's voice"},{"time":74000,"text":"and the rippling groove of the banjo."},{"time":78000,"text":"And after being totally and completely obsessed"},{"time":82000,"text":"with the mammoth richness and history"},{"time":84000,"text":"of Chinese culture,"},{"time":86000,"text":"it was like this total relief"},{"time":90000,"text":"to hear something so truly American"},{"time":93000,"text":"and so truly awesome."},{"time":96000,"text":"I knew I had to take a banjo with me to China."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101000,"text":"So before going to law school in China"},{"time":103000,"text":"I bought a banjo, I threw it in my little red truck"},{"time":106000,"text":"and I traveled down through Appalachia"},{"time":109000,"text":"and I learned a bunch of old American songs,"},{"time":111000,"text":"and I ended up in Kentucky"},{"time":113000,"text":"at the International Bluegrass Music Association Convention."},{"time":116000,"text":"And I was sitting in a hallway one night"},{"time":119000,"text":"and a couple girls came up to me."},{"time":121000,"text":"And they said, \"Hey, do you want to jam?\""},{"time":123000,"text":"And I was like, \"Sure.\""},{"time":125000,"text":"So I picked up my banjo"},{"time":127000,"text":"and I nervously played four songs that I actually knew with them."},{"time":130000,"text":"And a record executive walked up to me"},{"time":132000,"text":"and invited me to Nashville, Tennessee to make a record."}]},{"cues":[{"time":135000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":142000,"text":"It's been eight years,"},{"time":146000,"text":"and I can tell you that I didn't go to China to become a lawyer."},{"time":150000,"text":"In fact, I went to Nashville."},{"time":152000,"text":"And after a few months I was writing songs."},{"time":155000,"text":"And the first song I wrote was in English,"},{"time":157000,"text":"and the second one was in Chinese."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":164000,"text":"[Chinese]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":174000,"text":"Outside your door the world is waiting."},{"time":176000,"text":"Inside your heart a voice is calling."},{"time":178000,"text":"The four corners of the world are watching,"},{"time":180000,"text":"so travel daughter, travel."},{"time":183000,"text":"Go get it, girl."}]},{"cues":[{"time":185000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":194000,"text":"It's really been eight years since that fated night in Kentucky."},{"time":198000,"text":"And I've played thousands of shows."},{"time":200000,"text":"And I've collaborated"},{"time":202000,"text":"with so many incredible, inspirational musicians around the world."},{"time":206000,"text":"And I see the power of music."},{"time":208000,"text":"I see the power of music"},{"time":210000,"text":"to connect cultures."},{"time":212000,"text":"I see it when I stand on a stage"},{"time":214000,"text":"in a bluegrass festival in east Virginia"},{"time":216000,"text":"and I look out at the sea of lawn chairs"},{"time":218000,"text":"and I bust out into a song in Chinese."},{"time":221000,"text":"[Chinese]"},{"time":224000,"text":"And everybody's eyes just pop wide open"},{"time":227000,"text":"like it's going to fall out of their heads."},{"time":230000,"text":"And they're like, \"What's that girl doing?\""},{"time":232000,"text":"And then they come up to me after the show"},{"time":235000,"text":"and they all have a story."},{"time":237000,"text":"They all come up and they're like,"},{"time":239000,"text":"\"You know, my aunt's sister's babysitter's dog's chicken went to China"},{"time":243000,"text":"and adopted a girl.\""},{"time":245000,"text":"And I tell you what, it like everybody's got a story."},{"time":249000,"text":"It's just incredible."},{"time":252000,"text":"And then I go to China"},{"time":254000,"text":"and I stand on a stage at a university"},{"time":257000,"text":"and I bust out into a song in Chinese"},{"time":259000,"text":"and everybody sings along"},{"time":262000,"text":"and they roar with delight"},{"time":264000,"text":"at this girl"},{"time":266000,"text":"with the hair and the instrument,"},{"time":268000,"text":"and she's singing their music."}]},{"cues":[{"time":272000,"text":"And I see, even more importantly,"},{"time":276000,"text":"the power of music to connect hearts."},{"time":279000,"text":"Like the time I was in Sichuan Province"},{"time":282000,"text":"and I was singing for kids in relocation schools"},{"time":285000,"text":"in the earthquake disaster zone."},{"time":287000,"text":"And this little girl comes up to me."},{"time":290000,"text":"[Chinese]"},{"time":296000,"text":"\"Big sister Wong,\""},{"time":298000,"text":"Washburn, Wong, same difference."},{"time":302000,"text":"\"Big sister Wong, can I sing you a song"},{"time":305000,"text":"that my mom sang for me"},{"time":307000,"text":"before she was swallowed in the earthquake?\""},{"time":311000,"text":"And I sat down,"},{"time":313000,"text":"she sat on my lap."},{"time":315000,"text":"She started singing her song."},{"time":318000,"text":"And the warmth of her body"},{"time":321000,"text":"and the tears rolling down her rosy cheeks,"},{"time":325000,"text":"and I started to cry."},{"time":328000,"text":"And the light that shone off of her eyes"},{"time":332000,"text":"was a place I could have stayed forever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":336000,"text":"And in that moment, we weren't our American selves,"},{"time":339000,"text":"we weren't our Chinese selves,"},{"time":341000,"text":"we were just mortals"},{"time":345000,"text":"sitting together in that light that keeps us here."},{"time":350000,"text":"I want to dwell in that light"},{"time":354000,"text":"with you and with everyone."},{"time":356000,"text":"And I know U.S.-China relations"},{"time":358000,"text":"doesn't need another lawyer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}